    "The study of deep learning AES models that provide scores and associated feedback is limited.",
    "As a result, few of the existing survey papers only cover feedback in relation to",
    "Table 1 Comparison of survey papers on deep learning-based AES",
    "deep learning-based AES models.",
    "However, Wang et al. (2022a) conducted a systematic literature review on papers that specifically focus on evaluating argumentative essays and providing associated feedback."
